  "transliteration": "Anā fī ṭabʿī insēn bsīṭ barsha fī libistī. Mā nḥebbsh naṣraf barsha flūs ʿalā el-ḥwāyej, khāṭer nshūfhā mūsh ahamm ḥāja fī d-dunyā. Ahamm ḥāja ʿandī hiya er-rāḥa, mūsh es-stīl wela el-mōḍa. Bel-ḥaqq mā narkkzesh barsha fīl-alwān amma b-ṣifa ʿāmma nakhtār alwān muḥāyda kīma el-akḥal, kīma esh-shakhma wela el-abyaḍ. Sāhlīn bāsh tilbishom mʿa bʿaḍhom.\nFīsh-shtēʾ eṭ-ṭaqs fī Almānya bāred yoqtel, ʿalā hādhāka dīma nilbes jāketāt ghlīḍha bāsh nibqā dēfī. Taḥt el-jāketāt nilbes maryūl ṣūf skhūn w-srwēl ṭwīl, ʿādatan ykūn jīnz. Mā nḥebbsh nilbes barsha ṭabaqāt bāsh mā nitfallaqsh.\nFīṣ-ṣīf el-ḥkāya titbaddel bel-koll. Nilbes kēn pōlō khafīf w-shorṭāt. Nḥebb el-alwān el-fētḥa kīf el-abyaḍ wela el-bēj, khāṭerhā mā tsheddsh es-skhāna. Amma sāʿāt yaʿjebnī lōn mʿayyen, fa-nishrī pōlō b-lōn ākher, mathalan azraq, blū syēl wela akhḍar. El-muhem ykūn pōlō qṭon w-mrīyaḥ. W-fī sāqayya nilbes ṣandāl khafīf.\nAmma fīr-rbīʿ wela fīl-khrīf, el-jaww marra bēhī, marra khāyeb, yaʿnī mutaqalleb. Fīl-waqt hādha, el-ḥall el-mithālī ben-nisba līya huwa el-qomṣān. Nḥebb barsha nilbes qamīṣ bsīṭ, mathalan abyaḍ wela azraq, mʿa jīnz w-sbadrī. Nshūfhā libsa anīqa w-ʿamaliyya fī nafs el-waqt, tnajjem timshī bīhā lel-khedma wela tokhroj bīhā mʿa aṣḥābek. Mā nḥebbsh nʿaqqedhā barsha. Fil-lekhkhar, el-libsa lāzemhā tkūn ḥāja tkhallīk tḥess rūḥek mirtēḥ fī ḥayātek el-yawmiyya, mūsh maṣdar qalaq w-flūs ḍāyʿa."
}', '2025-07-27 23:30:46.555196', '2025-07-27 23:30:46.555198', true);







